<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>وَعَلِيهِ كَفَّارَة يَمِين<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span>أَي مثلهَا وَلَا تتَوَقَّف على الْوَطْء<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
